                  <summary>Parchment codex leaf from Egypt with a homily. Homily is about sins and quotes another text that is possibly apochryphal. Homily is addressed to a sinner. Has a picture of a bird drawn in the lower margin on the recto</summary>
                  <msItemStruct>
                     <note type="general">Actual dimensions of item are 16.0 x 26.7 cm</note>
                     <note type="general">71 lines</note>
                     <note type="general">Written in two columns in brown, red and metallic ink</note>
                     <note type="general">Lower margin of 4.5 cm.; left margin of 2.5 cm. on the recto; right margin of 2.5 cm. on the verso</note>
